we regularly post great inspiration, tips, tutorials, and videos.\r\n\r\n<strong>Stick around, you’ll find some great stuff. </strong>[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"You have any recommendations for what DSLR I should buy?\" open=\"false\"]Yes! Soon! Exclamation![/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"Can you recommend a photographer?\" open=\"false\"]Yes! Soon! More exclamation!\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][/vc_tab][vc_tab title=\"Partnering with Us\" tab_id=\"1419946039455-3-10\"][vc_toggle title=\"I’d like to advertise on 52Frames!\" open=\"false\"]Not a question, but we appreciate the enthusiasm. We work hard to ensure we deliver high-quality, highly-targeted ads to our users. We respect our users, and insist on working only with advertisers who do as well. Interested in learning more? Send us an email at <a href=\"mailto:help@52frames.com\">help@52frames.com</a>.\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"How can I sponsor a Weekly Challenge?\" open=\"false\"]First, have something awesome to offer our users. There are a limited number of Weekly Challenges (52, actually), so we want to make sure that the ones that are Sponsored are ones that fill us with pride to present. Second, be in touch.\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"I’ve been around the block, and have some great content to offer your community. Can I?\" open=\"false\"]Possibly! Let’s talk. We love offering tailored, high-quality content to our users. We’re open to all sorts of partnerships. <a href=\"mailto:info@52frames.com\">Let’s talk</a>.\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"I heard something about Photo Tours? I think we may be interested in something like that...?\" open=\"false\"]Hey there, explorer! Mosey on over to the Photo Walks section of the FAQ.\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][/vc_tab][vc_tab title=\"Photowalks\" tab_id=\"1419946224299-4-3\"][vc_toggle title=\"Photowalks? What that?\" open=\"false\"]Photowalks are walks where we take photos. Right? Right.\r\n\r\nOk, here’s more. Every month, in cities around the world, we get together to explore a bit and take some photos. This has a few great benefits: It gets us off our butts and into the real world. It connects us - in person - with our community. It allows us to see how other people shoot, and be immediately inspired. It will help you get married. (No joke! 2 of our Tel Aviv Framers got married after meeting at a photowalk!). Learn more about the photowalks, and sign up for one in your city, <a href=\"/photowalks\">here</a>.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"You don’t have a photowalk in my city. What’s up with that?\" open=\"false\"]There’s absolutely nothing to photograph in your city. Just kidding! Want to organize your own photowalk? We’ll give you whatever support you need and help others find you. Be in touch with us to discuss. Email <a href=\"mailto:photowalks@52frames.com\">photowalks@52frames.com</a>.\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"What about photo tours? Do you lead those?\" open=\"false\"]We’re planning potential global tours in the future. In the meantime, if you’re visiting Tel Aviv and want us to run a photo tour for you here, email us at <a href=\"mailto:photowalks@52frames.com\">photowalks@52frames.com</a> and we can work it out for you. Same goes if you want to propose photo tours anywhere else in the world, we have amazingly talented photographers from around the globe, and we can make some connections for you.\r\n\r\n[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"Do I have to be a member of 52Frames to join the photowalk?\" open=\"false\"]Nope! All are welcome! No fancy camera required! We may have some tours that have limited spaces, in which we’ll give first access to Framers, but our main goal here is to spread photolove![/vc_toggle][/vc_tab][/vc_tour][vc_column_text]<i>If you’re a member looking for even more FAQs about how the site works, hop on over to the </i><i>Members FAQ</i><i> page.</i>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','FAQ','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-12-30 13:34