d the Rule of Thirds</span>\r\n\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;More dramatic composition - get closer, get lower etc&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,9025,[null,0],null,null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11]\">Dramatic Composition - Make Your Photo Stand Out From the pack</span>\r\n<h4><span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;Exposure&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,25411,[null,0],[null,2,14277081],null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11,1]\">Exposure</span></h4>\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;Auto with Exposure Compensation (Exposure 101 - Knowing when and how to expose - too dark, turn to the right, too light turn to the left :)&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,9025,[null,0],null,null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11]\">Exposure Compensation - Quickly Control Your Exposure <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(Coming Soon!)</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;Metering Modes&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,9025,[null,0],null,null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11]\">Metering Modes - How Your Camera Understands Light <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(Coming Soon!)</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;Shutter Speed (and Tv)&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,9025,[null,0],null,null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11]\">Shutter Speed - Freeze the Action or Let it Blur <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(Coming Soon!)</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;Aperture (and Av)&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,9025,[null,0],null,null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11]\">Aperture - Get that Bright Beautiful Bokeh <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(Coming Soon!)</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"[null,2,&quot;ISO&quot;]\" data-sheets-userformat=\"[null,null,9025,[null,0],null,null,null,null,null,0,null,1,0,null,null,null,11]\">ISO - It\'s Time to get 